spells.description: Use: Receive cryptic instructions from somewhere in the Twisting Nether to reveal your next task. It's probably nothing, so complete it to gain 9,013 Intellect for 15 sec.  (1 Min 30 Sec Cooldown)

Equip: Carefully balance the Egg's incubation. While stationary, gain 100 Intellect every 1 sec, up to 30 times. Diminishes while moving. While moving, gain 113 of your highest secondary stat every 1 sec, up to 30 times. Diminishes while stationary. 

Additional stacks above 20 grant 60% reduced benefit.
Use: Suspend the Egg's incubation state for 20 sec. (2 Min Cooldown)
Equip: Assume a martial stance based on the last weapon drawn.

Use: urekian Flourish 
Conjure dual swords from the Arsenal to rend your target, dealing 705,280 Shadow damage over 3 sec. Gain 338 Parry and 225 Avoidance until the next weapon is drawn.
 (1 Min Cooldown)
Equip: Accumulate dark power from the Spellforge every 15 sec to empower your next rcane Barrage to deal 73,671 additional Shadow damage.

Use: Recklessly intensify the power of the Spellforge, multiplying its current damage by 125% until shortly after leaving combat, up to 5 times. At full power, gain 830 Haste for 6 sec when empowering your rcane Barrage. 

Beware glimpses of the Unseeming. (1 Min Cooldown)

spells.description: Equip: Receiving healing from allies has a high chance to restore 6,250 mana to your ally and grant you both 279 Versatility for 10 sec.

Cooldown reduced by 60 sec if this effect kills the target. (2 Min Cooldown)

Dealing Nature damage has a chance to grant you an additional dose.

Equip: Taking damage greater than 25% of your health grants you 1,801 Avoidance and increases healing taken by 10% for 10 sec. This effect may only occur every 90 sec.

Falling damage reduced.
